snippet.title: Let's Play - Gumchu Girl (Demo) Gameplay Playthrough
snippet.description:
The sequel of Gum Girl.
Solve puzzles and traverse through the cosmos. It's war against Kactus Kid and his army of veggies!

Play "Gumchu Girl" Here: https://caseportman.itch.io/gumchu-girl-demo

Like, Share, and Subscribe if you like the video!
More new games coming soon!

Check out my playlist for more games I've played!
